Package xxl.core.relational.metaData

This package provides the classes that are needed for describing the metadata of the relational algebra operators.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ColumnMetaData This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set.
 

Class Summary
AppendedResultSetMetaData Appends a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to each other and returns a new ResultSetMetaData object.
ColumnMetaDataResultSetMetaData This class provides relational metadata as specified by the ResultSetMetaData interface.
ColumnMetaDatas This class provides static methods for dealing with instances implementing the interface column metadata.
DecoratorColumnMetaData This class provides a decorator for a result set's column metadata.
MergedResultSetMetaData This abstract class is a ResultSetMetaData skeleton that wraps a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to a single one.
ProjectedResultSetMetaData Makes a projection of a result set metadata object to certain columns.
RenamedColumnMetaData Makes a renaming of a result set's column metadata.
RenamedResultSetMetaData Makes a renaming of a result set metadata object's columns.
ResultSetMetaDataColumnMetaData This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set by wrapping the result sets metadata.
ResultSetMetaDatas This class provides static methods for dealing with instances implementing the interface result set metadata.
StoredColumnMetaData This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set.
UnifiedResultSetMetaData Appends a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to each other and returns a new unified ResultSetMetaData object such that all column names are unique.
WrappedResultSetMetaData This class provides an extended decorator for metadata of the type ResultSetMetaData.
 

Package xxl.core.relational.metaData Description

This package provides the classes that are needed for describing the metadata of the relational algebra operators. This package extends the functionality of the classes ResultSetMetaData.
